Package: midlines
Title: Estimate Polygon Midlines
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Richard",
           family = "Patterson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "richard-patterson@hotmail.co.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8563-6053"))
Description: Estimates the midline of polygons provided in sf format. The package uses Voronoi tessellation to estimate the midline and offers some functions that can help to clean the lines.
